{"type": "article", "id": 25283, "title": "师法自然，韩国这个地下室有着意外的美景", "description": "设计师解释了他的创作意境如 Tom Waits 的歌“The piano has been drinking, not me”", "date": "2016-04-12T07:02:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 26084, "name": "地下空间"}, {"id": 1012, "name": "自然"}, {"id": 26086, "name": "景观"}, {"id": 26085, "name": "TUNEplanning"}], "category": 17, "author": 451727, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 216, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702130501BcaxKMXjfQ520tmY.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>位于韩国首尔钟路区平仓洞（Pyeongchang-dong）的一个地下空间 Dayang Sanghoi，利用自然环境的环抱的石头和树，打造了”天然去雕饰“的意境。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130456NBC6LwGb8dehKciZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这个地下空间由 TUNEplanning 设计，面积 84 平方米左右，最初被规划为展览馆，而后经过几次修改，改造成办公室、公司培训基地、餐厅、咖啡馆，现在成了一个可以举办多样休闲聚会活动的空间，可以说是它之前调整过的功能的合集。这也是它叫 Dayang Sanghoi 的原因，Dayang 在韩语里表示多样。</p>\n<p> Dayang Sanghoi 所在的平仓洞被北汉山（Bukhansan）环抱，陡峭的花岗岩和坚韧的松树构成了主要视觉形象，这也成为这个地下空间的景观主题。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130456OljNBL5KARiYWDdC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>这个地下空间和户外的岩石自然景观亲密接触，从门窗外看过去即是满目的岩石。室内的墙以金属框架支撑，填充石块和木炭，以流通地下空间潮湿的空气。天花板是用胶合板层叠表现的树木年轮纹样，还有一截松树枝自然伸进来垂下。</p>\n<p>设计师解释了他的创作意境如 Tom Waits 的歌“The piano has been drinking, not me”。空间隐喻表达了“是墙倾斜了还是人倾斜”。家具随意摆放，以看起来像是自然造就的。</p>\n<p>门窗外是满目的岩石。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130457brRmQKeuogV9sdtJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.44927536\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130457bBAVtZvdnL8zcRIw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>填充石块和木炭的墙。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130458ZYupGSgsVwBOclLv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>树木年轮天花板，一截松树枝自然伸进来垂下。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130458zNDwyiZ9mqBcOeh2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47492625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p class=\"\">夹层的舞台。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130459x4NnRldBpsyW8ur2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.47710487\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">家具任意摆放。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130500D4b3d8uSZiyMtIoE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49700599\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">整栋建筑。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130500TvCf9DFIEg2QjNpR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">平面图</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702130501u2ljQ3OEqFH0CX6n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70648148\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">题图和文内图来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/785045/dayangsanghoi-tuneplanning/57049ce8e58ece858d0001d6-dayangsanghoi-tuneplanning-photo\">archdaily</a><br></p>\n\n"}